warming on catchment response change (1993) Journal of Hydraulic, Coastal and Environmental Engineering, 489, pp. 1-10. , in Japanese with English abstract; Williams, M.W., Losleben, M., Caine, N., Greenland, D., Changes in climate and hydrochemical responses in a high-elevation catchment in the Rocky Mountains, USA (1996) Limnology and Oceanography, 41, pp. 939-946; Wolford, R.A., Bales, R.C., Hydrochemical modelling of Emerald Lake watershed, Sierra Nevada, California: Sensitivity of stream chemistry to changes in fluxes and model parameters (1996) Limnology and Oceanography, 41, pp. 947-954","Fukushima, T.; Dept. of Civil and Envirl. Eng., Faculty of Engineering, Hiroshima University, 1-4-1, Kagamiyama, Higashihiroshima, Hiroshima 739-8527, Japan; email: fukusima@ipc.hiroshima-u.ac.jp",,,,,,,,08856087,,HYPRE,,"English","Hydrol. Processes",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0034723967
